    <thetext>Description of problem:
Dell XPS 15 (9550) with external USB 3.0 dock: Since kernel 4.8.6 a &quot;shutdown&quot; does not turn off the machine. Worse, when manually turning it off with long-press of power button (at end of shutdown sequence as well as while Gnome is running) turns off the machine, but some 5-10 secs later it automatically turns on again.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
4.8.6 &amp; newly released 4.8.7</thetext>
